  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0db1\u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wildlife facilities for the people coming from Yala for the Kataragama parade",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thousands of devotees from the Eastern Province are coming on foot through the Yala forest for the historic Asala Maha Perahera held annually at the Kataragama temple.",
        "Minister Mahinda Amaraweera advised the Director General of Wildlife to prepare a special program for the facilities needed by those people and to protect them from wild animals.",
        "Accordingly, the Wildlife Department has started a special program to protect the devotees from drinking water and other facilities as well as wild animals.",
        "Necessary financial allocations have been allocated for this purpose."
      ],
